+# Markdown Preview Express App
+
+A small Node.js and Express web app for rendering Markdown into HTML on the same page.
+
+## Run locally
+
+```bash
+npm install
+npm start
+```
+
+The app runs on port `5005` by default:
+
+```text
+http://localhost:5005
+```
+
+To use a different port, set the `PORT` environment variable before starting the app.
