I noticed one local-runnability issue in the session cookie name: the `__Host-` prefix only works when the cookie is always `Secure`, which conflicts with plain HTTP local testing. I’m adjusting the cookie name while keeping `HttpOnly`, `SameSite`, and production `Secure` behavior.
